  <brief_title>Preoperative Pain and POCD in Elderly Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Chronic Pain Increases the Risk of Early Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Elderly Patients Undergoing Hip Joint Replacement Surgery: a Prospective Observational Cohort Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
